dataset.description: An array of objects that can be used to populate series and axes data using their dataKey property.

xAxis.description: The configuration of the x-axes. If not provided, a default axis config is used with id set to DEFAULT_X_AXIS_KEY.

yAxis.description: The configuration of the y-axes. If not provided, a default axis config is used with id set to DEFAULT_Y_AXIS_KEY.
